headline: Bowl Slop? Cava CEO Doesn’t Want to Hear It
summary: Cava Chief Executive Brett Schulman is taking a stand in defense of the bowl.  Cava and other restaurant chains such as Sweetgreen and Chipotle had a tough 2025.  Cava’s shares have fallen about 35% in the past 12 months.
